THIS SOFTWARE MODIFIES CRITICAL WINDOWS SYSTEM ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES.

By using this software, you acknowledge and accept the following:

1. SYSTEM MODIFICATION RISKS
   This software directly modifies the Windows PATH and PATHEXT environment
   variables, which are critical system configuration settings. Incorrect
   modifications can result in:
   - Applications failing to start or function correctly
   - System instability or boot failures
   - Loss of access to command-line tools
   - Inability to run scripts or executables
   - Other unpredictable system behavior

